{"tid":1536534,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"＜緊急物資＞想救前線命　一定要有！！！","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T00:10:12.000Z","uid":191271,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cd6658011f6c80f041dc0cbfa9d7a4e875bd410d","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:21:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>隨身ＣＡＭ！隨身ＣＡＭ！隨身ＣＡＭ！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU8qk3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU8qk3b.jpg&h=cbe62ecd&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">宜家班狗冇可能會比機會你睇ＣＣＴＶ<br />\n亦冇可能比你渣住手機影住走佬、救人、甚至被瘋狂打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似太子站，記者唔在場被人打死都冇人知，<br />\n真正既死無對證</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K88RgBx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK88RgBx.png&h=f5c5d42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">班狗隻隻都有隨身ＣＡＭ，點解我地冇！！！一個都冇</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>隨身ＣＡＭ拍到既一條片可能就救返一條手足既命！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"10f6852aec772a2be210d08249c5ea324ad84447","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"d7da022c8abee34ca5fec0e723f11c9891946f49","tid":1536534,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e6e13fef42b4bd41fa9446a5ef0ff35238520b6","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10c3700697d42502cec615efc18a60b9776f8a8","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f4ccd13930f94ad02ceee0a12090c8c38ecc63","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse