"Fa有得啦掛？<br />\n<br />\n同埋宜家企係度都暴動架啦<br />\n口罩都有意圖犯罪<br />\n<br />\n你有隱藏cam既叫做真相大白，冇就死無對證"},{"pid":"a8c7b29e25df4b12d267fcab3c9bccdecb33d058","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49bc6ede01f93e5017cfedd6a625d8dfbc59f7b6","tid":1536534,"uid":76355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:32:53.000Z","msg":"推，可以autosave上cloud更好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"呢句就岩聽<br />\n咁易被狗開到你個cam咩？<br />\n咁手機都係證據啦"},{"pid":"4b87ea9e0c570b14ff0ec342027fc6b2ba98d637","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625e1c1ae1fabaf9c889a3a46aad354e94db449b","tid":1536534,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>中央「三春袋」不能碰</strong></div></span></span><br />\n中國國務院港澳辦發言人楊光29日表示，一國兩制是個完整概念，一國是本、是根，根生才能葉茂，有三條底線不能觸碰，一是絕不允許任何危害國家主權安全行為、絕不允許挑戰中央權力、絕不允許香港對內地進行滲透破壞，他強調這三條紅線不可觸碰。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">楊光頭兩點都有話香港。<br />\n但值得留意，楊光講話沒有更多涉及官方絕不允許香港對內地進行滲透破壞的內容。<br />\n呢個我地睇到中共根本唔會理外國點諗，三條紅線無一條係勾結外國勢力。因為佢地同我地都知道外國係好難好難出兵幫香港。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但中共最怕係咩，就係內部人民搞革命。就好似Hunger game 入面，或者毛澤東既概念。</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">《星星之火，可以燎原》，原名《時局估量和紅軍行動問題》是中國共產黨紅四軍收到中共中央的「二月來信」後，林彪給毛澤東寫信，毛澤東回覆的一封公開信<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要做到更多影響力，就要影響我地最討厭既內地人。我地要分化內地人同中共政府。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190729-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E8%BE%A6%E6%8F%903%E5%BA%95%E7%B7%9A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%A8%A1%E7%B3%8A%E9%A1%AF%E6%AE%BA%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190729-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%258F%25903%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E7%25B3%258A%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=82aaeac5\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190729-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E8%BE%A6%E6%8F%903%E5%BA%95%E7%B7%9A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%A8%A1%E7%B3%8A%E9%A1%AF%E6%AE%BA%E6%A9%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">對在內地的內地人進行滲透</div></span></span><br />\nWe are formless. We are shapeless. We can flow. We can crash.  We are like water.  <br />\nWe are #Hongkongers!<br />\n<br />\n第一，我地係Formless，所以我地呢三個月所做既運動／革命都無一個official 名<br />\n禁既然我地係formless，我地呢場運動／革命都唔一定只有一個名，我地可以有無限個名。<br />\n英文可以叫water revolution<br />\n但中文 我地只要有個水字就係我地既名號<br />\n我地要利用中共怕事既方法 將所有文宣都加上#水<br />\n你可以叫呢場叫<br />\n水運動 <br />\n汽水運動<br />\n膠水運動<br />\n水泥運動<br />\n眼水運動<br />\n總之有個水字<br />\n仲有所有巴打一齊做，禁中共會入左一兩難局面<br />\n8964 5月35日 都可以block <br />\n但日常多變既字佢點block<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/egf0UmF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fegf0UmF.jpg&h=dca6ebfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「不許百姓飲水」增加敏感字眼 water revolution 水運動 #水 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dOoocS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dOoocS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">對已來港內地人地進行滲透</div></span></span><br />\n第二， 我地要令吃兩家茶禮既人 加入我地 或者被加入我地<br />\n幫已來港內地人<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">破釜沉舟</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我要攬炒 舉報每日150 嚟讀書工作嘅大陸人都被暴徒洗腦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dNPtqS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dNPtqS</a>"},{"pid":"90edc80d4b936d7fcb099aa527b6ef130188136e","tid":1536534,"uid":258572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"記得尖沙咀激安百幾蚊有一部"},{"pid":"71a5b429314f58d1cb201b3f96bc69514f57b91f","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90edc80d4b936d7fcb099aa527b6ef130188136e","tid":1536534,"uid":258572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"記得尖沙咀激安百幾蚊有一部"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"52c454fa36d1cce399f0028f8facbcdb0126550b","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">特別係救人果班，你拍既片可能就係歷史紀錄</span>"},{"pid":"861e571055bf1aff9233445cd2ce439c346c2994","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e519087a0114184ec14a0d71fa0cb4f79596ef","tid":1536534,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8c7b29e25df4b12d267fcab3c9bccdecb33d058","tid":1536534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49bc6ede01f93e5017cfedd6a625d8dfbc59f7b6","tid":1536534,"uid":76355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:32:53.000Z","msg":"推，可以autosave上cloud更好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"呢句就岩聽<br />\n咁易被狗開到你個cam咩？<br />\n咁手機都係證據啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"保密要做好<br />\n比狗搶到cam 都唔可以